OL,6,FLauren Wilkinson, senior policy
OL,7,Fresearcher at the PPI, said: "By their
OL,8,Flate 50s, women have average pension
OL,9,Fsavings worth less than two-thirds of
OL,10,Fmen's, with a substantial proportion
OL,11,Fof this difference stemming from
OL,12,Finequalities in the labour market,
OL,13,Fincluding differing working patterns
OL,14,Fand the gender pay gap.
