OL,3,CWomen 'need to work extra 19 years
OL,4,Ctypically to close pensions gender gap'
OL,6,FA Government spokesman said: "The
OL,7,Fsuccess of automatic enrolment has
OL,8,Ftransformed the UK pensions landscape
OL,9,Fand brought millions of women into
OL,10,Fpension saving for the very first
OL,11,Ftime, and our plans to expand
OL,12,Fautomatic enrolment ` by abolishing
OL,13,Fthe lower earnings limit for
OL,14,Fcontributions and reducing the age for
OL,15,Fbeing automatically enrolled to 18
OL,16,Fyears old ` will benefit women and low
OL,17,Fearners, once poorly served or
OL,18,Fexcluded from workplace pensions.
