OL,3,CWomen 'need to work extra 19 years
OL,4,Ctypically to close pensions gender gap'
OL,6,FJackie Leiper, managing director at
OL,7,FScottish Widows, said: "Far more needs
OL,8,Fto be done to tackle the gender
OL,9,Fpension gap ` our research says that
OL,10,Fright now, more than a third of women
OL,11,Fare not on track for even a minimum
OL,12,Fretirement lifestyle.
OL,14,F"Action must focus on putting the
OL,15,Fright measures in place for women to
OL,16,Fbe able to stay in high-quality
OL,17,Femployment whilst raising families,
OL,18,Fincluding improving access and funding
OL,19,Ffor childcare.
